Greg Hardy was convicted last July of beating, strangling and threatening to kill his ex-girlfriend, Nicki Holder .
Hardy was dropped by his previous team, the Carolina Panthers, because of these charges last year .
The NFL announced today that Hardy will be suspended without pay for 10 games at the start of the 2015 season .
Holder told police that Hardy choked her, slammed her against a bathtub, threw her to the floor and threatened to kill her after a fight .